&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About CGS&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;br&gt;With end-to-end capabilities, BlueCherry software enables many of the world’s most recognized fashion and apparel companies to manage critical business transactions and concept-to-consumer processes to improve speed to market, gain greater process visibility and control, increase productivity and operational efficiency, reduce costs, and enhance competitiveness.&lt;/p&gt;
