&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Summary Overview&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;br&gt;CGS’s Integrations Functional Consultants are responsible for leading and supporting client-facing integration initiatives as part of BlueCherry implementations. This role works closely with client’s business and technical stakeholders to design, configure, validate, and deploy integrations between BlueCherry and third-party platforms across eCommerce, wholesale, marketplaces, and custom systems.&lt;br&gt;The consultant serves as the functional subject-matter expert for BlueCherry integrations, translating business requirements into integration designs, validating data flows, supporting testing and go-live activities, and ensuring successful adoption of connected systems.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Primary Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Client Engagement &amp;amp; Solution Design&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Partner with clients to understand business processes, integration goals, and data requirements across eCommerce, wholesale, retail, and marketplace channels.&lt;br&gt;• Lead functional discovery sessions focused on integration scope, workflows, and exception handling.&lt;br&gt;• Translate business requirements into functional integration specifications and implementation approach.&lt;br&gt;• Act as a trusted advisor to clients on best practices for omni-channel and marketplace integrations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Integration Implementation &amp;amp; Delivery&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Configure and support implementations of the following BlueCherry integration modules:&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry Shopify B2B, B2C, and POS Connectors&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry NuOrder Connector&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry Amazon FBA and FBM Connectors&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry ChannelAdvisor Connector&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry JOOR Connector&lt;br&gt;o BlueCherry API for custom integrations&lt;br&gt;• Collaborate with technical teams to align functional requirements with technical integration design.&lt;br&gt;• Support data mapping, field-level validation, and end-to-end data flow testing.&lt;br&gt;• Lead and support integration testing cycles, including unit testing, system integration testing, and user acceptance testing.&lt;/p&gt;
