&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Training &amp;amp; Post-Go-Live Support&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;• Deliver client training on integration workflows, monitoring, and exception handling.&lt;br&gt;• Support hypercare and post-go-live stabilization activities.&lt;br&gt;• Provide knowledge transfer and documentation to clients and internal support teams.&lt;/p&gt;
